description: Do you like milkshakes and soda parlor drinks? Do you like ice cream trucks?If so, then you've come to the right place!Moovers and Shakers is a fresh twist on an old favorite - the ice cream truck!We come to where you are and serve you milkshakes and floats straight from our truck!A soda parlor on wheels, Moovers and Shakers is everything you loved about being a kid in one 16-oz cup of tasty, tasty treats.  We believe in providing high-quality, super-delicious milkshakes and soda parlor drinks -- or as we like to call them, Moovers and Shakers.  We believe customers are our neighbors and friends first -- and hey, that maybe all you hepcats have some wild ideas to share too.  We believe in spontaneous water balloon fights, bike races, and dance-offs.We believe in movin' and shakin' and doin' the twist, ya dig?
name: Moovers and Shakers
